A little girl asked her mother, "Can I go outside and play with the <br>
<br>
boys?" Her mother replied, "No, you can't play with the boys, <br>
<br>
they're too rough." The little girl thought about it for a few <br>
<br>
moments then asked, "If I can find a smooth one, can I play with <br>
<br>
him?" <br>
<br>
<br>
