At the beginning of a children's sermon, one girl came up to <br>
<br>
the altar wearing a beautiful dress. As the children were sitting <br>
<br>
down around the pastor, he leaned over and said to the girl, "That is a <br>
<br>
very pretty dress. Is it your Easter dress?" The girl replied almost <br>
<br>
directly into the pastor's clip-on mic, "Yes, and my Mom <br>
<br>
said it's a bitch to iron." <br>
