<br>
next to the barber chair, while her dad gets his hair cut, eating <br>
<br>
a snack cake. The barber says to her, "Sweetheart, you're gonna get <br>
<br>
hair on your Twinkie." She replied enthusiastically, "Oh I know! And <br>
<br>
Mommy says I'm gonna get boobs too!" <br>
